<body>
    <h1>Task 12 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"5b9018fa8f95" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-1.Intr=
oduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"cba72927f8b2" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.=
1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e9f8411ba6cf">This document provides a comprehensive technic=
al reference for implementing API monitoring dashboards and alerting for th=
e Bookstore API deployed on Amazon Web Services. The monitoring system is b=
uilt on New Relic APM and is designed to provide real-time visibility into =
API health, performance, and error behavior.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c11475463781">The monitoring system tracks the following key=
 signals:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8cb084d93162">Total API request count and request trends ove=
r time</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0fcd9591c758">HTTP response status codes (2xx, 4xx, 5xx)</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"96f5261a8698">Error rates and failure patterns</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"40322fe72bf6">API response time and latency trends</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c3af1fb1e380">The dashboard enables the operations team to q=
uickly identify failures, understand API behavior under load, and act on an=
omalies before they impact end users. This setup directly reduces Mean Time=
 To Detect (MTTD) and Mean Time To Resolve (MTTR) by surfacing actionable s=
ignals in a single, unified view.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a094b7442b0c"><strong>Intended Audience:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"783e89ff6043"><strong>CTO</strong> =E2=80=93 Strategic visib=
ility into API reliability and operational health</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6ae61bf61c6c"><strong>DevOps Engineers</strong> =E2=80=93 Da=
shboard configuration, alert management, and agent deployment</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"75fe9b9bac64"><strong>Cloud Engineers</strong> =E2=80=93 AWS=
 infrastructure integration with New Relic</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"86766454d446"><strong>Operations Team</strong> =E2=80=93 Day=
-to-day incident detection and response</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f20eb967206e"><strong>Developers</strong> =E2=80=93 API perf=
ormance awareness and error debugging</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"b4ba179c5824" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 =
Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b5b8783d9593">This document covers the following monitoring =
implementation:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dba7c8c25553">API observability using New Relic APM agent on=
 EC2</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a8ed09ca2e8d">HTTP status code monitoring (2xx, 4xx, 5xx bre=
akdown)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"72dad252fc3c">Error rate visualization and trend analysis</p=
></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0dc1b946d8ec">Dashboard creation for operational monitoring =
of the Bookstore API</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cd97587a0608">Alert configuration for API failures and abnor=
mal error rates</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b5571920a72f">Integration with AWS components =E2=80=94 Appl=
ication Load Balancer and EC2</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e9b529389d33"><strong>Out of Scope:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f125a7223026">Kubernetes monitoring</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a4f8549f8f9f">Distributed tracing implementation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b9057cd4754f">Advanced log analytics pipelines</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b1feb1be0c62">Enterprise-scale observability architecture</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"f1db7c064f17" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-2.Overviewofth=
eMonitoringProject">2. Overview of the Monitoring Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"e7ae8cfa4340" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition"=
>2.1 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ece188183ef9">API monitoring is the continuous process of tr=
acking the availability, performance, and response behavior of an API to en=
sure it is functioning correctly and meeting service level expectations. Ef=
fective monitoring provides early warning of degradation before it becomes =
an outage, and gives the operations team the context needed to diagnose and=
 resolve issues quickly.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f54f950b20eb">This monitoring implementation specifically de=
tects:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a8ffe7881879">API failures and service outages</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b4fe82c6a46d">Increasing error rates (4xx client errors and =
5xx server errors)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"68cc9cd78917">Abnormal or unexpected traffic patterns</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0e9e4b8a1112">Latency degradation and slow response times</p=
></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"b03dfb706fdc" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-2.2KeyPrincipl=
es=E2=80=93AWSWell-ArchitectedFramework">2.2 Key Principles =E2=80=93 AWS W=
ell-Architected Framework</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"0=
e3ee855-be53-42e9-a28d-0384a1e5aaff" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 535.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1264.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d02eef034b96">Pillar</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ee1b8f8fa2f3">How We Achieved It</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c9c95cd61f08">Operational Excellence</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2a3068eb2bde">Real-time dashboards and alerts provide immedi=
ate visibility into API health, enabling faster incident detection and stru=
ctured response</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7d51fcc76a51">Security</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2360d1a40e73">Monitoring surfaces suspicious traffic pattern=
s and abnormal API behavior =E2=80=94 such as sudden spikes in 4xx errors t=
hat may indicate unauthorized access attempts</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bd13efcfbaf1">Reliability</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2c86746978f0">Alerts on 5xx error rates and downtime ensure =
the team is notified immediately when the API is failing to serve requests<=
/p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"012af1bb9760">Performance Efficiency</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3e6059c700c9">Latency and response time monitoring identifie=
s slow endpoints and helps the team optimize API performance before user im=
pact</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"62a3899d0daf">Cost Optimisation</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"661f9c47a49b">Targeted monitoring prevents unnecessary auto-=
scaling triggered by false load signals =E2=80=94 ensuring resources are sc=
aled based on real demand</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"08a89baeb3bc">Sustainability</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6c66de453c66">Efficient, agent-based monitoring collects onl=
y the required metrics =E2=80=94 minimizing overhead on EC2 instances and a=
voiding unnecessary data ingestion costs</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"346553daf8e6" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObj=
ectives">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"abd306f2f0a0">Track total API request volume and request tre=
nds over time</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"712a27a47f66">Monitor HTTP response code distribution (2xx s=
uccess, 4xx client error, 5xx server error)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a424337f9f9c">Detect rising error rates and trigger alerts w=
hen thresholds are breached</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"762212f1ceb1">Visualize API response time patterns to identi=
fy latency degradation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5e82469a0d2a">Configure New Relic alerts for abnormal API be=
havior =E2=80=94 enabling proactive incident response</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"e703d178d957" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-2.4Constraints=
andAssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<p local-id=3D"88b96391ffcf"><strong>Constraints:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cc134a81ad03">Implementation time limited to 3 hours =E2=80=
=94 basic observability setup scoped accordingly</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6d6d41809ce9">Monitoring limited to API-level metrics =E2=80=
=94 infrastructure-level monitoring (EC2 CPU, memory) is out of scope for t=
his phase</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bac0186fc787">Limited historical data available due to the r=
ecent deployment of the Bookstore API</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6265ebdbbe06">New Relic free tier used =E2=80=94 data retent=
ion and alert policy limits apply</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"444d81d27b55"><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9f0fb8786a51">Bookstore API (FastAPI) is already deployed an=
d serving traffic on EC2</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3e209aeba0aa">New Relic agent is installed on the applicatio=
n server and configured with a valid license key</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c48b6f5025e8">Internet connectivity is available from the EC=
2 instance to the New Relic ingest endpoint</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c526da18c6da">API traffic is being generated during testing =
to populate dashboard metrics</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"faa060d3a112" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-3.Architecture=
andInfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"319324e3932d" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-3.1MonitoringA=
rchitecture">3.1 Monitoring Architecture</h2><span class=3D"confluence-embe=
dded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><im=
g class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-=
22-2026-6_03_08-PM-20260322-123332.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=
=3D"1056e38efdd2649eb96be7abe25256668b408c94d4319bd27939f94370de3316" data-=
image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1886978=
051/diagram-export-3-22-2026-6_03_08-PM-20260322-123332.png?version=3D1&amp=
;modificationDate=3D1774182889927&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-h=
eight=3D"910" data-width=3D"3464" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-=
linked-resource-id=3D"1885700937" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-l=
inked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"di=
agram-export-3-22-2026-6_03_08-PM-20260322-123332.png" data-base-url=3D"htt=
ps://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/=
png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1886978051" data-linked-resource-=
container-version=3D"2" data-media-id=3D"910cf16a-88ea-4c78-9aee-045940adc0=
35" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"122"></span>
<p local-id=3D"4ab87437e8c6"></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"7=
b871b36-7a26-40d0-b810-81b9d91d1745" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9039acf6eed6">Component</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"80f5ef43c432">Role</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"be57375cc14e">AWS EC2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ed0062250ea8">Hosts the FastAPI Bookstore application; New R=
elic agent installed directly on the instance</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"41a07a3b3621">AWS Application Load Balancer</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bcf579ab77b9">Distributes incoming API traffic across EC2 in=
stances; provides the request routing layer</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8a58cb7407a3">New Relic APM</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5dc3ad1d5b9f">Collects API metrics, error rates, and respons=
e time data; hosts dashboards and alert policies</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"20b6b5a7924e" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-3.2RequestMoni=
toringFlow">3.2 Request Monitoring Flow</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">User Re=
quest
      =E2=86=93
Application Load Balancer
      =E2=86=93
FastAPI Application Server (EC2)
      =E2=86=93
New Relic Agent (instrumented)
      =E2=86=93
New Relic Monitoring Dashboard</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"d04484b1ce4c">At each step, the New Relic agent intercepts a=
nd records:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c0e477832b59">Request count per endpoint</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a5a0c45cd504">HTTP response status codes returned</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f1292df0e7f9">Response time (latency) per request</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7e478aedd5bb">Error rate and exception details</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5bd727b0ab9e">This flow provides end-to-end visibility from =
the moment a request enters the load balancer to the final response returne=
d to the client.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"36d33456e20f" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-3.3Observabili=
tyComponents">3.3 Observability Components</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a=
7b43ab3-53e4-4dae-8d7c-5af3159ce6e5" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9620568d38c3">Pillar</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"65be4b9f29f8">Implementation</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f4f54ab0d9fb">Detail</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f9b782b12b05">Metrics</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0f4802da1797">New Relic APM</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0bce2f726a2f">Request count, error rate, status code distrib=
ution, response time</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a0092e95b9a2">Logs</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"73ba13a9c127">Application logging</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7826d271b85d">Python logging configuration captures applicat=
ion-level events and errors</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9a603641a764">Traces</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f79af250c723">Not implemented</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a23e71783484">Distributed tracing planned as a future enhanc=
ement</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"dc712fff190d" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-4.DashboardDes=
ign">4. Dashboard Design</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"eac8796aea82" id=3D"Task12-TechnicalDocument-4.1APIMonitori=
ngDashboard">4.1 API Monitoring Dashboard</h2>
<p local-id=3D"51d4253c52b1">The New Relic monitoring dashboard provides a =
unified view of API behavior using purpose-built visualizations for each ke=
y metric category.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a7b2d33fbf07"><strong>Design Principles:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fb1aea2c4a94">Clear and immediately actionable for the opera=
tions team</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9f52b9e6b578">Clean, minimal layout =E2=80=94 critical signa=
ls visible without scrolling</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c984961235dd">Metrics logically grouped by category: volume,=
 errors, and performance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"64e1aad57293">Real-time data refresh for live incident monit=
oring</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7aa2033c5a52"><strong>New Relic Agent Installation:</strong>=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"4411516e2a4b">Install the New Relic Python agent on the EC2 =
instance:</p>
<p local-id=3D"91df10db1dbb">bash</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">pip ins=
tall newrelic</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"e0d157812dc4">Generate the New Relic configuration file usin=
g your license key:</p>
<p local-id=3D"afe4b3621f69">bash</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">newreli=
c-admin generate-config &lt;YOUR_LICENSE_KEY&gt; newrelic.ini</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"ba5bbd769c7a">Start the FastAPI application with New Relic i=
nstrumentation enabled:</p>
<p local-id=3D"0df12fb1e068">bash</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">newreli=
c-admin run-program uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000</pre>
</div>
</div><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper =
confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image im=
age-center" alt=3D"image-20260321-141419.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy=
" src=3D"31ebd90caad15f7d0aac489ee6b9823ce1ddea0def6914ebad7b02daa94c2532" =
