<hr>
<p local-id=3D"93296e7ef105"><strong>Widget 4 =E2=80=94 Error Rate Monitori=
ng</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"bce6a3bf6f3b">Displays the percentage of failed requests ove=
r time. A rising error rate is the primary signal for alerting and incident=
 response.</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3605dfb59b22">Visualization: Billboard</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"78ab66fbdc1d">NRQL Query:</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7f9aa315231f">sql</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">SELECT =
percentage(count(*), WHERE error IS true) FROM Transaction TIMESERIES</pre>
</div>
