ration"><strong>6. Alert Configuration</strong></h2>
<p local-id=3D"ce42cda06678">Alerts are configured in New Relic to notify e=
ngineers immediately when API behavior becomes abnormal. All alerts are cat=
egorized by severity =E2=80=94 Warning for degraded performance, Critical f=
or active failures requiring immediate action.</p><span class=3D"confluence=
